show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/hgNCeU
show.description: A billionaire husband, betrayed and left for dead, returns in disguise as his wife’s bodyguard. In a world of love, lies and hidden truths, can Karan protect Seema while reclaiming his empire? When every glance hides a secret and every touch could be a betrayal, the battle between heart and survival begins.
